summary: An ordinance establishing, modifying and abrogating certain positions in the Buildings, Law, Engineering, Judicial (Traffic Court), Seattle-King County Public Health, Lighting and Water Departments; fixing compensations; superseding Ordinance 86700 (1958 Salary Ordinance) insofar as in conflict, and providing funds by budget item transfers and a reimbursable appropriation from the Emergency Fund, and declaring the emergency therefor.
